code: const{MongoClient}=require('mongodb');async function sendNewUser(data){const uri='mongodb://localhost:27017';const client=new MongoClient(uri);try{await client.connect();const database=client.db('baumna_data');const collection=database.collection('users');const result=await collection.insertOne(data);console.log("Data inserted with _id: ".concat(result.insertedId));}catch(error){console.error(error);}finally{await client.close();}}export default sendNewUser;
